MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: 06/25 - This mapping generates claim level detail data for the requested client. Includes all rebated claims from APC for all active QTRs till the period requested along with the associated fields from RPS staging if the claim is available in RPS and All submitted claims that have the post adjusted and new invoice associated will be loaded.
MAPPING.NAME: m_RPS_RPT_Insert_TCLM_RPT_DETL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.PERIOD_ID, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.RBATE_ID, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.RAC, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.EXTNL_SRC_CODE, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.EXTNL_LVL_ID1, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.EXTNL_LVL_ID2, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.EXTNL_LVL_ID3, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.EXTNL_LVL_ID4, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.EXTNL_LVL_ID5, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.NDC, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.DSPND_DATE, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.NABP_CODE, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.PICO_NO, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.RBATE_ACCESS, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.RBATE_MRKT_SHR, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.RBATE_ADMIN_FEE, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.EXCPT_STAT, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_TYPE, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_LVL1, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_LVL2, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_LVL3, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.INV_MODEL, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.INGRD_CST, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.FRMLY_ID, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.MEDD_CNTRC_ID, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.MEDD_PRTC_CD, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_GID, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CMS_PLAN_ID, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CORP_CD, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.MED_PYBL_CD, KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.TRAN_TYP_CD, KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.PICO_ID_NB, NVL(KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.CTRC_ID_NB, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CNTRL_NO) AS CTRC_ID_NB, NVL(KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.CG_NB, VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.XR007_CG_NB) AS CG_NB, KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.ACCS_RBAT_AMT, KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.MKSR_RBAT_AMT, KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.ADMN_FEE_AMT, TDRUG.BRND_NME, DECODE(UPPER(TDRUG_GDX.DRUG_PKG_UM_CD), 'EA','1','GM','2','ML','3') DRUG_PKG_UM_CD, CPAA106.CORP_NME, (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CLM_GID) FROM RPS.KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG ) RPS_CLM_CNT, SUM(CASE WHEN ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_GID) = 1 AND VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_GID = KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.CLM_GID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) OVER() RPSDM_CLM_CNT FROM RPS.VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY LEFT OUTER JOIN RPS.KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG ON (VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_GID = KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.CLM_GID AND VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.PERIOD_ID = KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.RBAT_BILL_PRD_NM AND KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.RPT_PRCS_NB = $$CURR_PRCS_NB) LEFT OUTER JOIN RPS.TDRUG TDRUG ON (VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.NDC = TDRUG.NDC_NB) LEFT OUTER JOIN RPS.CPAA106 CPAA106 ON (CASE WHEN KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.PICO_ID_NB IS NOT NULL THEN KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.PICO_ID_NB ELSE VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.PICO_NO END = CPAA106.PICO_ID_NB AND VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CORP_CD = CPAA106.CORP_CD) LEFT OUTER JOIN RPS.TDRUG_GDX TDRUG_GDX ON (VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.NDC = TDRUG_GDX.DRUG_NDC_ID) WHERE VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.PERIOD_ID BETWEEN '$$START_ACTIVE_QTR' AND '$$END_ACTIVE_QTR' AND VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.RBATE_ID IN ($$RBAT_IDs) -- Check to see if it should be equijoin or left outer join -- Equijoin for Payments and Collections -- Left Outer Join for Invoices Only (For Invoices only, the mainframe stage table will be empty) -- For Clearstone, CLM_SET_CD will be 1 AND (CASE WHEN $$CLM_SET_CD = 1 THEN 1 WHEN $$CLM_SET_CD = 2 AND VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_GID = KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.CLM_GID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = 1 -- Checking for Rebated Claims AND (CASE WHEN VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.EXCPT_STAT = 'R' THEN 1 WHEN VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.EXCPT_STAT = 'P' AND VAPC_DETAIL_ONLY.CLAIM_GID = KSRB335_RPT_CLM_STG.CLM_GID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = 1 WITH UR --
